SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0
2023-06-10 03:06:09.810 +02:00 [INF] Executing OkObjectResult, writing value of type '<>f__AnonymousType5`4[[System.String, System.Private.CoreLib, Version=6.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=7cec85d7bea7798e],[System.String, System.Private.CoreLib, Version=6.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=7cec85d7bea7798e],[System.String, System.Private.CoreLib, Version=6.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=7cec85d7bea7798e],[System.String, System.Private.CoreLib, Version=6.0.0.0, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=7cec85d7bea7798e]]'.

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0
